# Environment Configuration Examples

# ===== DEVELOPMENT =====
# When running locally with backend on port 8080
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080/api

# ===== PRODUCTION =====
# When deployed to production server
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api

# For music files to work properly:
# - Copy MP3 files to Backend/src/main/resources/static/music/
# - Database stores relative paths: /static/music/filename.mp3
# - Frontend automatically converts to full URL based on VITE_API_URL
# - This makes it compatible with all environments (localhost, staging, production)
